metadata.name: Sveti Tomaz
metadata.description:
Sveti Tomaž is a church in the village of the same name in the Selska valley where I live in the northwestern part of Slovenia near a medieval town of Škofja Loka. This church is a world-famous photographic motif.

3000 x 2000 px | 300 Dpi

The collector will receive a 30x21 signed fine art print anywhere in the world.
